data.description: Embrace the serenity of country living in this charming rancher nestled on .61 acres of picturesque landscape. This inviting home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a host of modern updates and neutral paint throughout. Step inside to discover LVP flooring, complemented by sleek granite countertops in the kitchen, offering both style and durability. Enjoy this beautifuly kept abode, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply unwinding in comfort. Outside, a detached oversized garage provides ample storage for vehicles and equipment, while offering endless possibilities for hobbies or workshops. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the surrounding views, where field views and open skies paint a stunning backdrop to everyday life. Don't miss this opportunity to experience the tranquility and charm of country living at its finest."
